@startuml EsecuzioneRuntime
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor White
skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor LightBlue
    BorderColor DarkBlue
}
skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor LightYellow
    BorderColor Orange
}

title Esecuzione Runtime Task (Mail vs Produzione)

participant "Hangfire Scheduler" as HF
participant "ProductionJobRunner" as Runner
participant "MailImportHandlerRegistry" as Registry
participant "Hera16EwsHandler" as Handler
participant "ServiceReadDataViaMail" as MailService
participant "LettoreDati" as Lettore
database "TaskDaEseguire" as DB
participant "Exchange Server" as Exchange
database "HERA16 Table" as TargetDB

HF -> Runner: 1. Triggered execution:\nRunAsync(idTaskDaEseguire)
activate Runner
Runner -> DB: 2. Carica entit‡ con Include:\nProcedura, Fase, navigazioni
Runner -> Runner: 3. IsMailTask(entity)?\nCheck MailServiceCode

alt Mail Task (MailServiceCode != null)
    Runner -> Registry: 4. Get(entity.MailServiceCode)\nResolve handler
    activate Registry
    Registry -> Handler: 5. Return Hera16EwsHandler\nper "HERA16.EWS"
    deactivate Registry
    
    Runner -> Handler: 6. ExecuteAsync(scope, context, ct)\ncon MailImportExecutionContext
    activate Handler
    Handler -> MailService: 7. ProcessHera16Async(ct)\nPipeline specifica HERA16
    activate MailService
    
    MailService -> Exchange: 8. FindItems(Inbox, filters)\nCerca email con soggetto specifico
    activate Exchange
    Exchange -> MailService: 9. Email results\ncon allegati CSV
    deactivate Exchange
    
    MailService -> MailService: 10. ProcessEmailAsync()\nEstrae e processa allegati
    MailService -> TargetDB: 11. BulkInsert CSV data\nSqlBulkCopy verso HERA16
    activate TargetDB
    TargetDB -> MailService: 12. Insert completed
    deactivate TargetDB
    
    MailService -> Handler: 13. Return record count
    deactivate MailService
    Handler -> Runner: 14. Return success count
    deactivate Handler

else Production Task (MailServiceCode == null)
    Runner -> Lettore: 4. SetDatiProduzioneAsync(dto)\nPipeline produzione standard
    activate Lettore
    Lettore -> DB: 5. Execute query con\nparametri configurati
    Lettore -> Runner: 6. Success response
    deactivate Lettore
end

Runner -> DB: 15. UPDATE audit fields:\nLastRunUtc, ConsecutiveFailures,\nLastError
deactivate Runner

note right of DB: Audit trail aggiornato\nper monitoring e debugging

@enduml